Content Elemets field that includes the use of Assets (as opposed to the standard file upload field.

{blog_content} 
  {assets} {files} <img src="{url}" /> {/files} {/assets} 
  {heading}{value}{/heading}
  {wygwam} {value} {/wygwam} 
  {wysiwyg} {value} {/wysiwyg} 
  {rich_text}{value}{/rich_text}
  {code} {value} {/code} 
{/blog_content}

